data.description: Waiting just for you!! Where city lights become your sunset, and convenience dances with luxury. Imagine sunrise jogs alongside the shimmering Silver Comet Trail, winding just behind your neighborhood like a silver ribbon promising adventure. Soon, its impending connection with the Beltline, will weave you into the vibrant tapestry of Atlanta's green heart.    This Hutton plan? Buckle up. An open-concept playground unfolds before you, seamlessly connecting gathering room, cafe, and sunroom - think sun-drenched mornings reading the paper, laughter-filled game nights, and cozy movie marathons. But wait, there's more! Your private rooftop loft awaits, boasting dual terraces perfect for sipping cocktails under the city's glittering embrace accompanied by charming bistro lights. Oh, and did we mention the gourmet kitchen with built-in appliances begging to unleash your inner chef? Ascetically pleasing, but durable luxury vinyl plank floors throughout the main-level? A bedroom on the lower-level with separate entrance and full bathroom for ultimate convenience?    Location? West Village and Ivy Walk are your new backyard, buzzing with shops, restaurants, and endless happy hours. Need a quick escape? 285 is a stone's throw away, ready to whisk you anywhere your heart desires.     4400 West isn't just a home, it's an invitation. An invitation to write your own city symphony, where luxury and vibrancy harmonize beautifully. Don't just live, thrive in this urban oasis.
